---
title: Chermoula Beef Meatballs with Carrot Couscous & Tomato-Cucumber Salsa
description: Get a load of this meal that's brimming with colour and flavour. With a fluffy (and sneaky) carrot couscous as the base for mildly spiced beef meatballs and a refreshing tomato salsa, all the elements come together for a delightful explosion of taste!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5e4dbaa7aac3ef5dd40f5f07-c0cc2717.jpg
